name: TIFA-PAPUA MUSICAL INSTRUMENTS (INDONESIA)
description:
Tifa is a typical musical instrument in Eastern Indonesia, especially Maluku and Papua. This musical instrument is shaped like a drum and is made of wood with a hole in the middle. There are several types of Tifa musical instruments such as Tifa Jekir, Tifa Basic, Tifa Cut, Tifa Jekir Cut and Tifa Bas
